{"tid":1513219,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警員涉騙6同袍逾8.3萬元　被控欺詐周五答辯","createTime":"2019-08-28T08:39:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T08:51:16.000Z","uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"da5b1967942e5aace898ad4203c69a7bd517d71a","tid":1513219,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T08:39:10.000Z","msg":"廉署落案起訴一名高級警員6項欺詐罪，涉嫌以欺詐手段，騙取6名警員合共超過83000元貸款。廉署准被告保釋，星期五在西九龍裁判法院答辯。<br />\n<br />\n49歲被告林仲文，案發時在深水埗分區一個巡邏小隊工作，他在2016年認識6名同於該巡邏小隊工作的警員。<br />\n　　 <br />\n控罪指，被告涉嫌於2018年4月至5月期間，先後10次不誠實地向6名同袍訛稱需要金錢支付母親在內地的醫療費，並意圖詐騙誘使對方向他提供10筆共超過83000萬元的貸款，被告從每名警員取得的款項由大約6千元至25000元不等。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477317-20190828.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477317-20190828.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5OTO5ApsLFANoEfWU0iq%2Bkc%3D&h=bbc54ff2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477317-20190828.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ec45e825\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477317-20190828.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"f876c9d589842514423ae54ef204d6f28b2561df","tid":1513219,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T08:39:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">求幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n(極正經) 關注被控義士進程請入，一個也不能少不是口號！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1512095\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1512095</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3bfa254a5d81333038f8bca3b4c7216d60ba55c6","tid":1513219,"uid":168703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T08:40:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yYSNtf8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.l